      input(type="checkbox")
      p Check one item
    .item
      input(type="checkbox")
      p Hold down your Shift key
    .item
      input(type="checkbox")
      p Check a lower item
    .item
      input(type="checkbox")
      p Everything in between should also be set to checked
    .item
      input(type="checkbox")
      p Try to do it without any libraries
    .item
      input(type="checkbox")
      p Just regular JavaScript
    .item
      input(type="checkbox")
      p Good Luck!
